{"tid":3727,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"第一身足球遊戲BALL3D","createTime":"2016-11-26T08:51:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T13:30:43.000Z","uid":14593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37b12e0f04d82c053699e3a0f7247424994abc60","tid":3727,"uid":14593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:51:31.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.ball3d.com/images/logo-ball3d.png?nowe2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ball3d.com%2Fimages%2Flogo-ball3d.png%3Fnowe2&h=1c6cbaa8&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">由一名波蘭人Mariusz Kowalczyk開發&amp;#22021;網頁3D足球遊戲 - Ball3D<br />\n你&amp;#22021;足球哲學係以個人之力帶領隊友爭勝定係團隊配合？<br />\n無論點，你都可以係呢度實踐！</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.ball3d.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ball3d.com&d=qm%2FKAUzScOk9DORplP4uFMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=7a7e9f91\" target=\"_blank\">www.ball3d.com</a> &lt;-官方網址</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://ball3dhk.wix.com/2015\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fball3dhk.wix.com%2F2015&d=qm%2FKAUzScOk9DORplP4uFMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=f661b138\" target=\"_blank\">http://ball3dhk.wix.com/2015</a> &lt;-香港Ball3D玩家聯誼網</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDjBp4iFUlmzfMJgZGpoq0A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCDjBp4iFUlmzfMJgZGpoq0A&d=qm%2FKAUzScOk9DORplP4uFMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=7772073e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDjBp4iFUlmzfMJgZGpoq0A</a>  &lt;-巴打們自製遊戲片段</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://ball3dhkleague.wixsite.com/b3dhk2016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fball3dhkleague.wixsite.com%2Fb3dhk2016&d=qm%2FKAUzScOk9DORplP4uFMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=5f4e0cb7\" target=\"_blank\">http://ball3dhkleague.wixsite.com/b3dhk2016</a> &lt;-香港ball3d聯賽網</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCM7VR1BYNmd2JGY3QjLplsw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCM7VR1BYNmd2JGY3QjLplsw&d=qm%2FKAUzScOk9DORplP4uFMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=0a20b9b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCM7VR1BYNmd2JGY3QjLplsw</a> &lt;-香港ball3d聯賽入球片段</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">每名玩家各自操控一個圓形人仔比賽。傳、停、帶、射、拉西由你掌握<br />\n初次玩會自動被要求安裝<strong>unity web player plugin</strong>，裝完就玩得！建議使用firefox玩，會較順</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.ytimg.com/vi/BQzXoemW8Fs/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FBQzXoemW8Fs%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=627480f3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>控制方法</strong></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">WASD=上下左右移動、MOUSE移動=控制視角、左鍵=禁實蓄力 放開就會踢走個波、SPACE空格/右鍵= 跳躍、SHIFT = 挑高個波、QE/mouse rotation=拉西、Tab/Esc = 去menu/離開房間/options、enter= 同所有人講野 等等</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">目前多數逢晚上9點後都會有人開香港場，亦建議新手得閒可自行熟習玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />g <br />\n因為隻Game對初學者黎講太新鮮, 需較長時間掌握基本技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />g </div>"},{"pid":"1e12c403439a2441c082f46aae8d12ef3fe1728b","tid":3727,"uid":14593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:52:47.000Z","msg":"[BALL3DHK] BALL3D教學系列-基本操作教學 (1)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oGXsD5iWAt4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoGXsD5iWAt4&d=qm%2FKAUzScOk9DORplP4uFMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=21b971ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oGXsD5iWAt4</a><br />\n<br />\n[BALL3DHK] BALL3D教學系列-基本操作教學 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rD_xr_QxPmQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrD_xr_QxPmQ&d=qm%2FKAUzScOk9DORplP4uFMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=3b51f1aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rD_xr_QxPmQ</a><br />\n力度控制, 地波, CURVE <br />\n<br />\n[BALL3DHK] BALL3D教學系列-基本操作教學 (3) SHIFT<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=efISzh2vYrY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DefISzh2vYrY&d=qm%2FKAUzScOk9DORplP4uFMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=9b075250\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=efISzh2vYrY</a><br />\n用SHIFT 過人,笠射笠傳<br />\n<br />\nBALL3D公認球王nak skill+goal compilation<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9bO57yXof10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9bO57yXof10&d=qm%2FKAUzScOk9DORplP4uFMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=e515714a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9bO57yXof10</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Command:</strong><br />\n較球場背景<br />\n/tribunes 0 &lt;&lt;冇人入場既球場<br />\n/tribunes 1 &lt;&lt;有約30000人入場既球場<br />\n/tribunes 2 &lt;&lt;乜都冇<br />\n<br />\n較挑波招式<br />\n/old_shift 0 &lt;&lt;粒波挑起後會比較離身, 適合用於笠傳, 笠射<br />\n/old_shift 1 &lt;&lt;粒波挑起後會比較貼身, 適合用於盤扭, 過人"},{"pid":"20777baaa8b56448dd3758a1b0329716fedca525","tid":3727,"uid":14593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:53:49.000Z","msg":"FAQ: <br />\nQ:建議新手一開始玩咩位置<br />\nA:後防, 因為打後一般比前面多波掂, 同埋職責主要係做下清波閘波等 多波掂,新手自然可以藉此練下基本功。打好基本功, 到時打前場做攻擊手就事半功倍<br />\n<br />\nQ:點樣加快傳波/射波時既球速?<br />\nA:鬆開power制前跳一跳。以中短距離傳球為例, 如果齋禁power制傳波, 球速會比較慢, 較容易被對方截到波。而跳既幅度就會影響到粒波既軌跡(e.g. 跳得越高, 粒波越貼地)  <br />\n<br />\nQ:點樣射波大力又唔會飛機? <br />\nA:射波之前跳躍 因為同波既接觸面高左 就唔會飛機 可以控制跳躍時機而踢出地波/中腰波<br />\n<br />\nQ:點解踢個波好似有DELAY咁? <br />\nA:你一日禁實蓄力制 佢未爆POWER都唔會射個波出去 所以個波到既時候你就要放制射出去 <br />\n<br />\nQ:守門員好難做/好難擋波 <br />\nA:因為MOUSE左鍵係蓄力制 你可以係咁禁制 食一食個波 咁就唔會MISS左個波彈唔到 <br />\n<br />\nQ:好難落西 <br />\nA:慣左射波跳躍個控制先 落西係BONUS野 只係射既時候加左Q/E制<br />\n<br />\nBALL3D仲有好多技巧學 例如撞牆 SOMBRERO 笠死等 <br />\n可以請教場上既高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n快D黎玩啦"},{"pid":"4e32c94367925586355586d6cae1b9b6bf73113a","tid":3727,"uid":14593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38d0413d8732390997a1299393145a342af533b","tid":3727,"uid":14593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T12:57:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85ad27a02f79aee39b5be4d329ec1af1565d981","tid":3727,"uid":14593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T14:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10813367e3538d26f2de529dbd6cf65127bebbe9","tid":3727,"uid":14593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T04:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f645f5c663e1217ab86cdbfacb94a09ee925f6","tid":3727,"uid":14593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d0e5a351917c333b91cba32ef415c99986c5a8","tid":3727,"uid":14593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187208531314c56b6f2c7b5e95aa902d91961186","tid":3727,"uid":14593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T13:14:17.000Z","msg":"有場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd7d9e827f62b4608e14403cf2cf9dedaab3d33","tid":3727,"uid":14593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.g